{"word":"προοράω","slug":"προοράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προοράω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-όψομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-εόρᾱκα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> aor2 <a href='S:προεῖδον'><el>προεῖδον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to see before one, see what is just before the eyes</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <i>to look forward to</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to look before one</i> or <i>forward</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to see before, foresee</i>, <el>τὸ μέλλον</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>τὸ προορᾶν σευ</el> your <i>foresight</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to provide</i> or <i>make provision for</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in attic also in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> and plup. <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, <i>to look before one</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to foresee</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to provide for</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}